title: NES Project 2003 (NES games/music, anime)
description:
A collection of music videos with remixed NES audio. Videos are made by mixing together captures from the games themselves and an anime picked by the creator. Some of the soundtracks are very lightly edited, while others are completely redone but still in the style and feel of the original.

Sized to fit on CD-R. MP3 2 channel audio, DIVX video, variable bitrate. Runtime 1:21:36 (H:MM:SS)
